bindsym $mod+$alt+Ctrl+k workspace $wsB
bindsym $mod+$alt+Ctrl+l workspace $wsC
bindsym $mod+$alt+Ctrl+p workspace $wsD

## Navigate // Next Workspace // <◇> Tab ##
